 T\u0161et\u0161eeniast ja Uljanovskist p\u00e4rit Vene s\u00f5durid|trans-title=Ukraine:In Crimea there are Russian troops from Chechnya and Ulyanovsk|publisher=Postimees|language=et|date=5 March 2014|accessdate=16 September 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"Interest\">{{cite news|last1=Interest|first1=The National|title=Get Ready, America: Russia Has Its Own Deadly 'Delta Force'|url=http://nationalinterest.org/blog/the-buzz/get-ready-america-russia-has-its-own-deadly-delta-force-19793|accessdate=12 April 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"Crimea, 2014\">{{cite book|last1=Galeotti|first1=Mark|title=Spetsnaz: Russia's Special Forces|date=2015|publisher=Osprey Publishing|location=Oxford, UK|isbn=978-1-4728-0722-9|pages=50|edition=Elite|url=https://ospreypublishing.com/spetsnaz-russia-s-special-forces|accessdate=11 April 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Main Intelligence Directorate (Russia)#Activities|22nd Spetsnaz Brigade]]\n* [[45th Detached Reconnaissance Regiment|45th Guards Spetsnaz Regiment]]\n| units2      = {{Flagicon image|Ensign of the Ukrainian Ground Forces.svg}} [[Ukrainian Ground Forces|'''Ground Forces''']]:\n* [[Territorial defence battalion (Ukraine)|Territorial defence battalions]]\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Airmobile troops of Ukraine.svg}} [[Ukrainian Air Assault Forces|'''Air Assault Forces''']]<br />{{flagicon image|Ensign of the Ukrainian Air Force.svg}} [[Ukrainian Air Force|'''Air Force''']]<br />{{flagicon image|Naval Ensign of Ukraine.svg}} [[Ukrainian Navy|'''Navy''']]<br />{{flagicon image|Flag_of_the_National_Guard_of_Ukraine.svg}} [[National Guard of Ukraine|'''National Guard''']]:\n* [[Right Sector]]\n* [[Azov Battalion]]\n* [[Donbas Battalion]]\n[[File:\u0413\u0435\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u0434\u0438\u0447\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u0437\u043d\u0430\u043a - \u0435\u043c\u0431\u043b\u0435\u043c\u0430 \u041c\u0412\u0421 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0438.svg|20px]] [[Special Tasks Patrol Police (Ukraine)|'''Special tasks patrol police''']]:\n* [[Dnipro Battalion]]\n* [[Kharkiv Police Battalion|Kharkiv Battalion]]\n[[File:Emblem of the State Border Guard Service of Ukraine.svg|20px]] [[State Border Guard Service of Ukraine|'''State Border Guard''']]:\n* [[Noman \u00c7elebicihan Battalion]]\n[[File:Security Service of Ukraine Emblem.svg|20px]] [[Security Service of Ukraine|'''Security Service''']]:\n* [[File:Alpha SBU emblem.png|20px]] [[Alpha Group (Ukraine)|Alpha Group]]\n[[File:Emblem of the Ukrainian special forces.png|20px]] [[Special Operations Forces (Ukraine)|'''Special Operations Forces''']]\n| strength1   = {{flagicon|Russia}} '''Russian Forces in Crimea''' (\"[[Little green men (Ukrainian crisis)|Little green men]]\"):<br />25,000\u201330,000 (2014)<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/04/world/europe/ukraine-russia-tensions/|title=Ukraine looks for 'sign of hope' from Russia over Crimea|publisher=CNN|author=Greg Botelho|author2=Diana Magnay|author3=Phil Black|date=5 March 2014|accessdate=11 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pravda.com.ua/news/2014/03/7/7018027/|script-title=uk:\u0412 \u041a\u0440\u0438\u043c\u0443 \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0431\u0443\u0432\u0430\u044e\u0442\u044c \u0432\u0436\u0435 30 \u0442\u0438\u0441\u044f\u0447 \u0440\u043e\u0441\u0456\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0445 \u0432\u0456\u0439\u0441\u044c\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0445 - \u043f\u0440\u0438\u043a\u043e\u0440\u0434\u043e\u043d\u043d\u0438\u043a\u0438|trans-title=Already 30 thousand Russian military personnel in Crimea in the capacity of border guards|language=uk|work=[[Ukrayinska Pravda]]|date=7 March 2014|accessdate=11 January 2015}}</ref><br />{{flagicon image|Naval Ensign of Russia.svg}} '''Black Sea Fleet''':<br />11,000 (including [[Russian Naval Infantry|Marines]])<br />30 + Warships<br />(incl. [[Soviet submarine B-871|submarine]])<br />4 Squadrons of fighter aircraft<br />(18 planes each)<br />'''Reinforcements''': 16,000 (March 2014)<ref name=\"Beast\">{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/03/01/so-russia-invaded-crimea.html|title=Russia Stages a Coup in Crimea|newspaper=The Daily Beast|date=3 January 2014|author=Michael Weiss|accessdate=11 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/04/world/europe/ukraine-mood-on-the-ground/index.html?hpt=bosread|title=An eerie mood on the ground in Crimea |publisher=CNN |accessdate=30 December 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Lizzie Dearden|title=Ukraine crisis: Putin asks Russian parliament's permission for military invasion in Crimea|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/ukraine-crisis-putin-asks-russian-parliaments-permission-for-military-invasion-in-crimea-9162253.html|newspaper=The Independent|date=1 March 2014|accessdate=11 January 2015|location=London}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://interfax.com.ua/news/general/194157.html|script-title=ru:\u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u044f \u043d\u0435\u0437\u0430\u043a\u043e\u043d\u043d\u043e \u0443\u0432\u0435\u043b\u0438\u0447\u0438\u043b\u0430 \u0447\u0438\u0441\u043b\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0441\u0432\u043e\u0438\u0445 \u0432\u043e\u0439\u0441\u043a \u0432 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0438\u043d\u0435 \u0434\u043e 16 \u0442\u044b\u0441. \u2013 \u0438.\u043e. \u043c\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430 \u043e\u0431\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u044b|language=ru|trans-title=Russia illegally increased the number of its troops in Ukraine up to 21 thousand - Acting Minister of Defence|agency=Interfax.ua|date=3 March 2014|accessdate=11 January 2015}}</ref>\u201342,000<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/insider-view-moscow-control-ukraine-crimea-article-1.1708580|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306053739/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/insider-view-moscow-control-ukraine-crimea-article-1.1708580|archivedate=6 March 2014 |title=Insider's view: Moscow is in control of Crimea in Ukraine|date=3 March 2014|work=Daily News|location=New York|accessdate=6 March 2014}}</ref><br