ovsk]] to [[Luhansk]]\n| result      = '''Ongoing:'''\n* Unmarked Russian troops take over Crimea, seize military units,<ref name=\"uk.reuters.com\">{{Citation|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/04/17/russia-putin-crimea-idUKL6N0N921H20140417|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419015007/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/04/17/russia-putin-crimea-idUKL6N0N921H20140417|url-status=dead|archive-date=19 April 2014|title=Putin admits Russian forces were deployed to Crimea|newspaper=[[Reuters]]|date=17 April 2014|quote=\"We had to take unavoidable steps so that events did not develop as they are currently developing in southeast Ukraine. ... Of course our troops stood behind Crimea's self-defence forces.\"}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/world/ukraine-puts-troops-on-high-alert-threatening-war-20140303-hvfsx.html?skin=text-only|title=Ukraine puts troops on high alert, threatening war|newspaper=[[The New York Times]]|agency=Reuters|author=Alison Smale|date=3 March 2014|accessdate=11 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Putin admits unmarked soldiers in Ukraine were Russian; optimistic about Geneva talks|url=https://www.pbs.org/newshour/rundown/putin-admits-unmarked-soldiers-ukraine-russian-optimistic-geneva-talks/|publisher=PBS|author=Willis Raburu|date=17 April 2014|accessdate=30 December 2014}}</ref> fortify near [[Chonhar]], [[Kherson Oblast]]<ref name=\"feb27\">{{cite web|url=http://gazeta.ua/ru/articles/np/_dorogi-v-krym-perekryli-blokpostami-kotorye-ohranyaet-berkut-i-vooruzhennye-lyudi-v-kamuflyazhe/544741|script-title=ru:\u0414\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0433\u0438 \u0432 \u041a\u0440\u044b\u043c \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u043a\u0440\u044b\u043b\u0438 \u0431\u043b\u043e\u043a\u043f\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043c\u0438, \u043a\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0440\u044b\u0435 \u043e\u0445\u0440\u0430\u043d\u044f\u0435\u0442 \u0411\u0435\u0440\u043a\u0443\u0442 \u0438 \u0432\u043e\u043e\u0440\u0443\u0436\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0435 \u043b\u044e\u0434\u0